      <h2 class="section__title anamate">The roles</h2>
      <p class="section-sub-title anamate">We’re seeking not 1, but 3 digital enthusiasts for an 18-month contract within 3 areas: Social, Influencer and Affiliates. You’ll work for 6 months in each, as part of an award-winning Direct to Consumer team. <br/><br/>Here’s what you’ll be doing in each role…</p>
