      <h3 class="job-card__title">Social Media Assistant</h3>
      <div class="text-block__list-col">
        <ul>
          <li>Responsible for setting the social media community strategy for:</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Instagram - posts and stories</li>
            <li>Facebook - posts</li>
          </ul>
          <li>Planning and scheduling the social media content calendar</li>
          <li>Working with the Paid Performance Agency on paid promotion</li>
          <li>Working with the in-house Creative Studio to create social media assets</li>
          <li>Monthly reporting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <button class="btn apply">Apply now<img src="{{ 'paw.png' | asset_img_url: '30x' }}" alt="Paw silhouette"></button>
    </article>
    
    <article class="text-block text-block--white job-card anamate">
      <div class="job-card__number"><span>3</span></div>
      <h3 class="job-card__title">Affiliates Assistant</h3>
      <div class="text-block__list-col">
        <ul>
          <li>Engaging and networking with a broad range of affiliates across cashback, loyalty, content and social</li>
          <li>Putting together a quarterly plan of affiliate offers to gain extra exposure for the channel and drive sales in seasonal sale periods</li>
          <li>Weekly and monthly reporting for the channel, with focus on new customer acquisition numbers and Cost Per Action</li>
          <li>Working on one strategic partnership (with support from Acquisition Lead) per month</li>
          <li> Collaboration with SEO Lead on how we can work with content partners to further our organic reach and growth</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <button class="btn apply">Apply now<img src="{{ 'paw.png' | asset_img_url: '30x' }}" alt="Paw silhouette"></button>
